OL,3,CChancellor urged not to raise taxes on
OL,4,C'drained' businesses in Budget
OL,6,FBut in a submission to Ms Reeves ahead
OL,7,Fof the announcement, the BCC urged the
OL,8,FChancellor to steer clear of
OL,9,Fincreasing taxes on companies, arguing
OL,10,Fbusiness confidence had still not
OL,11,Frecovered from last year's rises.
OL,13,FBCC director-general Shevaun Haviland
OL,14,Fsaid firms felt "drained" and could
OL,15,Fnot plan ahead as they expected
OL,16,F"further tax demands to be laid at
OL,17,Ftheir feet".
