OL,3,CChancellor urged not to raise taxes on
OL,4,C'drained' businesses in Budget
OL,6,FMs Haviland said: "Last year's budget
OL,7,Ftook the wind from their sails, and
OL,8,Fthey have been struggling to find
OL,9,Fmomentum ever since.
OL,11,F"The Chancellor must seize this moment
OL,12,Fand use her Budget to deliver a pro-
OL,13,Fgrowth agenda that can restore
OL,14,Foptimism and belief amongst business
OL,15,Fleaders."
OL,17,FShe added: "This year's Budget will be
OL,18,Fa make-or-break moment for many firms."
