OL,3,CChancellor urged not to raise taxes on
OL,4,C'drained' businesses in Budget
OL,6,FAs well as calling for a commitment to
OL,7,Favoid further increases taxes on
OL,8,Fbusinesses, the BCC's submission urged
OL,9,Fa reform of business rates and the
OL,10,Fremoval of the windfall tax on oil and
OL,11,Fgas introduced by the last government.
OL,13,FIn more than 60 recommendations, the
OL,14,Findustry body proposed further
OL,15,Finfrastructure investment, cuts to
OL,16,Fcustoms barriers and action on skills
OL,17,Fshortages, including a wage subsidy
OL,18,Fscheme for young people with long-term
OL,19,Fhealth issues.
