OL,6,FLabour has made much of its plans to
OL,7,Fapprove 150 major infrastructure
OL,8,Fprojects by the next election, and has
OL,9,Falready pledged to support expansions
OL,10,Fof both Heathrow and Gatwick airports
OL,11,F` another of the BCC's requests.
OL,13,FAnd while the Treasury would not
OL,14,Fcomment on Budget speculation, a
OL,15,Fspokesperson for the department
OL,16,Finsisted the Chancellor would "strike
OL,17,Fthe right balance" between ensuring
OL,18,Ffunding for public services and
OL,19,Fsecuring economic growth.
