OL,6,FAll these factors have led some
OL,7,Feconomists to suggest Ms Reeves will
OL,8,Fneed to find another #40 billion if
OL,9,Fshe is to keep meeting her targets `
OL,10,Fand #50 billion if she is to restore
OL,11,Fher previous headroom.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, the Government insists that
OL,14,Fit will stick to its manifesto pledge
OL,15,Fnot to increase income tax, national
OL,16,Finsurance or VAT, narrowing her
OL,17,Foptions for raising revenue.
